  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group for Micromobility",
  "purpose": "To discuss regulation in the micromobility sector as part of decarbonising our transport system; discuss good regulation and practice already taking place and where it can be improved; identify where government can include micromobility regulation in upcoming legislation; advocate for safety of pedestrians and road users in relation to micromobility.",
